text: Manayunk can refer to: *Manayunk, Philadelphia, a neighborhood in the U.S. city of Philadelphia, Pennsylvania *USS Ajax (1869), a former U.S. Navy vessel originally named USS Manayunk *USS Manayunk (AN-81), a former U.S. Navy net laying ship *Pretzel Park in Philadelphia, formerly known as Manayunk Park.
title: Manayunk
